{#def missing #}
<div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-md">
  <div class="card-body">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Here's what we have so far</h2>
    <div class="alert alert-warning">
      <span>
        We still don't know {{ missing | join(", ") }}, so we can't
        run a full program screening yet.
      </span>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm mt-3">
      That's okay &mdash; you can start over any time with a bit more
      detail. In the meantime, your local
      <a href="https://www.211.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
         class="link">211 helpline</a>
      or mutual aid network can point you toward help right away.
    </p>
    <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm mt-3">Start over</a>
  </div>
</div>
